Checkout code from GitHub

Build Docker image

Push image to ECR (or DockerHub)

Deploy API using Helm chart to EKS

Expose via Kong automatically

-----------------------------------------------------------

Triggering on Code Change
In GitHub, set up a Webhook → Jenkins URL /github-webhook/ → triggers this pipeline automatically.
Add this in Jenkins job config:

Build Triggers → GitHub hook trigger for GITScm polling

Helm Upgrade ensures:

First deployment → installs chart

Next deployments → update with new Docker tag

Kong ingress ensures API is exposed at http://api.polaris.com
